        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 13. Dichotomius sagittarius (Harold, 1869) stat. rev. A–B. Dorsal habitus. A. ♁. B. ♀. C. Lateral view of the aedeagus.D. Anterior view of the cephalic carina.E. Ventral view of aedeagus.F–G. Lamella copulatrix. H. Ventral view of the metacoxa, displaying on the posterior margin a single row of organized ocellate setigerous punctures." ;
